BeachCatalog.com is an online swimwear portal and a network of affiliate programs from participating swimwear designers.  Our affiliate network tracking system only tracks basic information if a final transaction is made so that we can identify your transaction and charge a negotiated fee to the appropriate designer. 
This notice applies to all information collected or submitted on the BeachCatalog.com's website. On some pages, you can make requests, and register to receive materials or information from our swimwear designers. The types of information collected at these pages may include:
User's Name
Email address from user or referred by user
Phone number for business requests
Business information for wholesale and/or advertising requests
Modeling-related information (not required).
